00:33:56,210 --> 00:33:59,210
MUSIC: Final notes of "Taps"

434
00:34:20,490 --> 00:34:25,990
Those of us who were connected
with the programme, most of us,

435
00:34:25,990 --> 00:34:30,930
thought that that was the end
of Last Of The Summer Wine.

