00:34:30,930 --> 00:34:36,050
And then, quite extraordinarily,
Roy Clarke, our author,

437
00:34:36,050 --> 00:34:40,030
wrote,
in the passage of three weeks,

438
00:34:40,030 --> 00:34:42,690
three episodes

439
00:34:42,690 --> 00:34:47,730
