Elegy For Fallen Wellies.

440
00:34:47,730 --> 00:34:50,930
They were the most touching,

441
00:34:50,930 --> 00:34:53,630
the most moving,

442
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:56,550
most hilarious programmes

443
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:59,270
that I've ever seen on television!

